    <item>
      <title>日产裁员 9,000 人，首席执行官薪酬减半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/nissan-cuts-9-000-jobs-slashes-ceo-s-pay-in-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于行业状况不佳和内部缺陷，日产将裁员 9,000 人并降低制造能力。由于业绩不佳，这家日本汽车制造商的首席执行官将失去一半的薪酬。彭博社的 Reed Stevenson 谈到了日产扭转局面的努力。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/nissan-cuts-9-000-jobs-slashes-ceo-s-pay-in-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求银行在沙特阿拉伯出售美元纸币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-mandates-banks-to-sell-dollar-notes-in-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国已授权银行在沙特发行美元债券，这是中国自 2021 年以来首次发行美元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-mandates-banks-to-sell-dollar-notes-in-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国债券市场关注重要立法会议的财政计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-bond-market-eyes-fiscal-plans-from-key-legislative-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国债券交易员正在关注本周的一次重要立法会议，预计立法者将在会议上批准一项价值数万亿元人民币的财政方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-bond-market-eyes-fiscal-plans-from-key-legislative-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:11:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产债务违约风险跃升至 2023 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本汽车制造商日产汽车公司大幅下调盈利预期并表示将裁员 9,000 人之后，该公司债务违约风险指标跃升，这加剧了人们对该公司信贷状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛克哈特：“有信心”美联储独立性将得到维护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/lockhart-confident-federal-reserve-independence-will-be-preserved</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前亚特兰大联邦储备银行行长丹尼斯·洛克哈特分享了他对央行决定将利率降低四分之一个百分点的看法。他还讨论了美联储的独立性。主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普连任，他不会辞职。洛克哈特在“彭博：亚洲交易”节目中发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/lockhart-confident-federal-reserve-independence-will-be-preserved</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场消化特朗普和中国影响 油价有望本周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着市场消化特朗普第二次当选总统的影响，包括是否会刺激第一大进口国中国扩大刺激措施，油价本周上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗 Atlas SP 新部门获得蓝筹评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/apollo-s-atlas-sp-gets-blue-chip-ratings-for-new-funding-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 的结构性信贷业务 Atlas SP Partners 已成立一家子公司来借钱，三大债券评级机构均给予该部门蓝筹信用评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/apollo-s-atlas-sp-gets-blue-chip-ratings-for-new-funding-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:23:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后亚洲股市跟随美国股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美联储降息影响，美国股市、债券和大宗商品均出现上涨，亚洲股市周五也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
